Description. Habitus (
Fig. 6
). Large and robust species, body length 23.4 mm , width 5.0 mm. Dorsum dark brown to black, shiny, underside dark brown to black, legs, antennae, and palpi dark brown.

Bionomics. Type specimen was collected in a maple-beech forest on highly pronounced karstic landforms at altitudes of 680–705 m (
